OL,3,CFirst Minister Mark Drakeford faces
OL,4,Cmany more questions after he steps down
OL,6,FEven though is standing down as first
OL,7,Fminister of Wales, the questions he
OL,8,Fhas faced today to the UK Covid
OL,9,FInquiry about his handling of the
OL,10,FCovid pandemic won't be the last.
OL,12,FIn the short term, next Tuesday - 19
OL,13,FMarch - will be the final time he will
OL,14,Fanswer First Minister's Questions in
OL,15,Fthe Senedd.
OL,17,FFor the last two Tuesdays, he has been
OL,18,Funder fire from the leaders of the
OL,19,FWelsh Conservatives and Plaid Cymru
OL,20,Fand there is no reason to expect that
OL,21,Fwon't be any different next week.
