OL,3,CFirst Minister Mark Drakeford faces
OL,4,Cmany more questions after he steps down
OL,6,FBoth used their questions to ask about
OL,7,FMr Drakeford's use of WhatsApp.
OL,9,FThat in itself is no surprise:
OL,10,FWhatsApp messages have been at the
OL,11,Fcentre of the inquiry and of political
OL,12,Fcriticism directed at Boris Johnson,
OL,13,FMatt Hancock, Nicola Sturgeon and
OL,14,Fothers.
OL,16,FOn both occasions in the Senedd, Mr
OL,17,FDrakeford refused to answer because,
OL,18,Fhe said, he had to respect the
OL,19,Finquiry. His refusal infuriated his
OL,20,Fopponents and led to increasingly
OL,21,Fangry exchanges.
