OL,3,CFirst Minister Mark Drakeford faces
OL,4,Cmany more questions after he steps down
OL,6,FWell, now they know. He told the
OL,7,Finquiry that he used WhatsApp on 11
OL,8,Foccasions, one of which was to say
OL,9,F"thank you".
OL,11,FMr Drakeford portrayed himself as
OL,12,Fsomeone who is largely ignorant of
OL,13,Fboth communications systems such as
OL,14,FWhatsApp and other technical aspects
OL,15,Fof mobile phones. He said he only has
OL,16,Fone phone, which was provided to him
OL,17,Fas part of his role as Senedd Member,
OL,18,Fnot as a Welsh Government minister.
