OL,3,CFirst Minister Mark Drakeford faces
OL,4,Cmany more questions after he steps down
OL,6,FBut here's why I predict another round
OL,7,Fof questions about his phone use. The
OL,8,Finquiry heard that any messages on his
OL,9,Fphone from July 2018 to March 2021 are
OL,10,Fnot recoverable.
OL,12,F"I have no knowledge or expertise in
OL,13,Fthe way in which messages are stored
OL,14,For not stored," he said.
