OL,3,CFirst Minister Mark Drakeford faces
OL,4,Cmany more questions after he steps down
OL,6,FHe also said he favours text messages
OL,7,F- the opposition leaders may want to
OL,8,Fknow about that - and, regardless of
OL,9,Fhis own limited use, he defended the
OL,10,Fuse of WhatsApp by ministers and
OL,11,Fofficials for informal communication
OL,12,Fduring the pandemic.
OL,14,FSome may think all that is a
OL,15,Fdistraction from the real issues. And
OL,16,Fthat is why in the longer term, even
OL,17,Fafter he has stepped down as first
OL,18,Fminister, I think Mark Drakeford will
OL,19,Fcontinue to face questions.
