OL,6,Fof the Covid-19 Bereaved Families for
OL,7,FJustice Cymru told my colleague, ITV
OL,8,FWales health reporter Katie Fenton,
OL,9,Fthat they will not be giving up in
OL,10,Ftheir fight for what they see as
OL,11,Fjustice.
OL,13,FShe said they will keep pushing for a
OL,14,FWales-specific Covid Inquiry. Could
OL,15,Fthe next First Minister take the
OL,16,Fopportunity to differentiate
OL,17,Fthemselves with an early decision to
OL,18,Fhold one?
